				p.articletext So how does VANISH work? Some of the Utilities in OBSCURITY's deck are Gadgets. By keeping your most valuable Gadgets hidden from your opponent, you'll be able to use them turn after turn. VANISH helps by turning your Gadgets face-down, meaning that opponents simply can't do anything until you turn them face-up again by using VANISH a second time. Let's check out a few examples.

