				p.articletext As you can see by the sub-type underneath the card titles, both Static Grenade and X-Ray Spex are Gadgets. That means that OBSCURITY can VANISH Static Grenades to turn it upside-down. Face-down Utilities are hidden from all players until they are turned face-up and using VANISH on face-down Gadgets will turn them face-up.

				p.articletext Both Static Grenades and X-Ray Spex have abilities that trigger each time you VANISH them. This ability will fire every time you VANISH the card, regardless whether it is face-up or face-down. There is no limit for the number of times you are able to VANISH a given Utility per turn, meaning that each of these Gadgets could fire 3 times or more per turn! 

				p.articletext Let's look at another example...

				.row.articlecardrow.text-center
					.col-md-6.articlecardpanel
